                            "name": "StewardShip Terms and Conditions",
                            "trackingId": "stewardship-terms-and-conditions",
                            "content": "\u003cp>\u003ch2 class=\"modalWindow_headline\">Terms - Benefits, Eligibility and Conditions\u003c/h2>\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_copy\">\n    Last updated August 30, 2023\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_title\">WINE.COM STEWARDSHIP\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_copy\">\nWelcome to the Terms and Conditions (&quot;Terms&quot;) for the StewardShip shipping membership program (StewardShip). These Terms are between you and Wine.com, Inc., and/or its affiliates (&quot;Wine.com&quot;), and govern our respective rights and obligations. The Terms, together with the applicable terms and conditions related to any promotional offers provided to you for use with StewardShip, constitute the entire agreement between you and Wine.com related to StewardShip. Please note that your use of the Wine.com website, mobile application, and StewardShip membership are also governed by our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, as well as all other applicable terms, conditions, limitations and requirements on the Wine.com website, all of which (as changed over time) are incorporated into these Terms. If you register for StewardShip membership, you accept these terms, conditions, limitations and requirements. Please read these Terms carefully.\n\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_title\">Program Benefits\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_copy\">\n    StewardShip members are entitled to free standard shipping on all eligible purchases.\n\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_title\">Eligible Purchases\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_copy\">\nFree standard shipping is limited to products sold by Wine.com on \u003ca href=\"http://www.wine.com\">www.wine.com\u003c/a> or Wine.com mobile application that are shipped to continental United States addresses, excluding U.S. territories, possessions and protectorates. We may exclude products in our discretion. Standard shipping is not available in Alaska or Hawaii, so your order will be sent using an expedited method. You will be credited for standard shipping and charged an additional amount necessary to upgrade to expedited shipping. The shopping cart will indicate the shipping method and total charge on the final review page.\n\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_title\">Conditions\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_copy\">\nYou must have a Wine.com account to register for and use StewardShip. We reserve the right to accept or refuse membership in our discretion. You may not transfer or assign your StewardShip membership or any StewardShip benefits, including promotion codes for StewardShip memberships or benefits, except as allowed in these terms. Changing or combining orders, or changing your shipping address, speed, or preferences might affect StewardShip eligibility. Please note: We may ship the products by ground or air at our discretion (these options do not correspond to any carrier-branded shipping services); Our carriers usually do not pick-up or deliver packages on weekends or holidays; Promo code is valid only on orders placed from the Wine.com account that purchased the StewardShip program. Code cannot be used on any other Wine.com account. In cases of extreme weather where only expedited shipping is available, you will receive a credit for the cost of standard shipping. StewardShip cannot be given as a gift because it is tied to the account of the person purchasing it. Instead, we recommend a gift certificate. Evening, date-specific and by appointment shipments will receive a credit for the cost of standard shipping. We may exclude products with special shipping characteristics at our discretion. Your Wine.com StewardShip membership does not apply to orders placed through our Corporate Sales team. StewardShip members are not permitted to purchase products for the purpose of resale, rental, or to ship to their customers or potential customers using StewardShip benefits. From time to time, Wine.com may choose in its sole discretion to add or remove StewardShip membership benefits.\n\u003c/p>\n\u003ch2 class=\"modalWindow_headline\">Terms - Changes, Termination and Liability\u003c/h2>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_title\">Agreement Changes\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_copy\">\nWine.com may in its discretion change and update these Terms, Wine.com&#39;s general Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, or any aspect of StewardShip membership, without prior notice to you. However, any increase in the membership fee will not apply until your membership is renewed. If you cancel your membership before the effective date of these changes, Wine.com will give you a prorated refund of your membership fee based on the number of full months remaining in your membership period. This refund option does not apply to any other changes Wine.com may make. If any change is found invalid, void, or for any reason unenforceable, that change is severable and does not affect the validity and enforceability of any remaining changes or conditions. YOUR CONTINUED MEMBERSHIP AFTER WINE.COM CHANGES THESE TERMS, TERMS OF SERVICE, PRIVACY POLICY, OR MEMBERSHIP CONSTITUTES YOUR ACCEPTANCE OF THE CHANGES. IF YOU DO NOT AGREE TO ANY CHANGES, YOU MUST CANCEL YOUR MEMBERSHIP.\n\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_title\">Termination by Wine.com\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_copy\">\nWine.com may terminate your membership at its discretion without notice. If we do so, we will give you a prorated refund based on the number of full months remaining in your membership. However, we will not give any refund for termination related to conduct that Wine.com determines, in its discretion, violates these Terms or any applicable law, involves fraud or misuse of this membership program, or is harmful to our interests or another user. Wine.coms failure to insist upon or enforce your strict compliance with these Terms will not constitute a waiver of any of its rights.\n\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_title\">Limitation of Liability\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_copy\">\nIN ADDITION TO OTHER LIMITATIONS AND EXCLUSIONS IN WINE.COM&#39;S TERMS OF SERVICE, IN NO EVENT WILL WE OR OUR DIRECTORS, OFFICERS, EMPLOYEES, AGENTS OR OTHER REPRESENTATIVES BE LIABLE FOR ANY DIRECT, INDIRECT, SPECIAL, INCIDENTAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, OR ANY OTHER DAMAGES OF ANY KIND, ARISING OUT OF OR RELATED TO STEWARDSHIP. OUR TOTAL LIABILITY, WHETHER IN CONTRACT, WARRANTY, TORT (INCLUDING NEGLIGENCE) OR OTHERWISE, WILL NOT EXCEED THE LAST ANNUAL MEMBERSHIP FEE YOU PAID. THESE EXCLUSIONS AND LIMITATIONS OF LIABILITY WILL APPLY TO THE FULLEST EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW AND WILL SURVIVE CANCELLATION OR TERMINATION OF YOUR MEMBERSHIP. CERTAIN STATE LAWS DO NOT ALLOW THE EXCLUSION OR LIMITATION OF CERTAIN DAMAGES. IF THESE LAWS APPLY TO YOU, SOME OR ALL OF THE ABOVE EXCLUSIONS OR LIMITATIONS MAY NOT APPLY TO YOU, AND YOU MIGHT HAVE ADDITIONAL RIGHTS.\n\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_title\">Fees; Renewal\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_copy\">\nThe annual membership fee for StewardShip is $69.00. This fee is non-refundable except as expressly set forth in these Terms. Taxes may apply on either or both of the membership fee and the reduced shipping charges for StewardShip and you are responsible to pay all such taxes. UNLESS YOU NOTIFY US BEFORE RENEWAL THAT YOU WANT TO CANCEL, YOU UNDERSTAND YOUR MEMBERSHIP WILL AUTOMATICALLY RENEW AND YOU AUTHORIZE US TO COLLECT THE THEN-APPLICABLE ANNUAL MEMBERSHIP FEE AND ANY TAXES, USING ANY PAYMENT METHOD WE HAVE ON RECORD FOR YOU, AND TO CHARGE ANY CREDIT CARD, DEBIT CARD, OR ANY OTHER PAYMENT METHOD THAT WE HAVE ON FILE FOR YOU ONE OR MORE TIMES, FOR FULL OR PARTIAL AMOUNTS, AS REASONABLY NECESSARY FOR US TO COLLECT THE PAYMENTS DUE FROM YOU.\n\u003c/p>\n\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_title\">Membership Cancellation\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_copy\">\nIf you cancel your membership before you have made any eligible purchases, we will refund your full membership fee. \n\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_title\">Promotional Trial Memberships\u003c/p>\n\u003cp class=\"modalWindow_copy\">\nWe sometimes offer certain customers various trial or other promotional memberships, which are subject to these Terms except as otherwise stated in the promotional offers. Trial memberships cannot be canceled, but trial members can at any time choose not to upgrade to regular annual membership at the end of the trial period.\n\u003c/p>\n",
